medalsthat Caloy has earned the hard way in the last five years.\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(Read everything about him in ourpeople page.\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Check the latest on theParis Olympics hereas well asupdated medal tally.)\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 968, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The historic feat of the 24-year-old star gymnast is an epic reminder of what is often neglected and forgotten in the world of sports: the value of support and platform for athletes, and their mental and emotional well-being.\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1195, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We followed Caloy's journey from hisworld championship goldin 2019 to his victories in theSoutheast Asian Gamesto his settling for bronze in Antwerp to his comeback in theDoha World CupandAsian Championships- and to whenhe fell shortin his signature floor exercise event in the 2021 Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1297, \"end\": 1302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999850406313, \"rank\": 7.928367672105598e-09, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1338, \"end\": 1345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antwerp\", \"score\": 0.9999983361326685, \"rank\": 8.682335667126275e-07, \"text\": \"Antwerp\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antwerp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antwerp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Watch Caloy in the2019 SEA Games here.)\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In an uncanny way, Tokyo was a moment that Caloy and the GOATSimone Bilesshared: a stumble that caused deep pain and broke them, albeit temporarily.\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999255264913373, \"rank\": 5.187496300589999e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Tokyo, Caloy had adisappointing finish;Biles dropped outat the opening event as she struggled with her mental health.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1690, \"end\": 1695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999255264913373, \"rank\": 5.187496300589999e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two got clobbered in the toxic universe that is social media.\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1873, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not help but compare their journeys as I was watching theNetflix documentary on Bileson Sunday.\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Both carried invisible injuries in their hearts and minds.\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 2035, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet, both were blessed with courage that made them choose to allow themselves time to heal.\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In May, two months before the Paris Olympics,Caloy decided to tell all in a heartwarming interviewwith Rappler sports editorJasmine Payoand reporterDelfin Dioquino.\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2232, \"end\": 2239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rappler\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had by then had afalling outwith his managers, he had left the world-class training facilities of Tokyo and returned to Manila, and he had been feuding with some family members.\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2395, \"end\": 2400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999255264913373, \"rank\": 5.187496300589999e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2417, \"end\": 2423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"score\": 0.9988538954617715, \"rank\": 0.001147221834934834, \"text\": \"Manila\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he found love.\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2494, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And he was home.\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And to him, that's all that mattered.\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He knew, Caloy told Rappler, that the only way to get back to his old competitive form was toclear his head,release his anger, andfind his joy.\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2693, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2570, \"end\": 2577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rappler\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That self-discovery explains the grace and focus that earned him -\\u00a0and his country - two golds.\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2789, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch thefull interview here.\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2819, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the other side of the world, aprisoner swapbetween Russia and the West reconciled traumatized detainees with their families.\", \"from\": 2821, \"to\": 2948, \"entities\"